  "3010170": {
    "name": "Fangtopia",
    "steam_appid": 3010170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《灵异乌托邦》是一款轻松休闲的建造/益智游戏，在这里你可以搭建各种光怪陆离的景观。从卡组中抽取六角形地块，打造可爱而灵异的南瓜王国，邀请怪物居民来到你的万圣节小镇！逃离现实，尽情享受这个无忧无虑、无惊无吓的新奇世界吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/81b268ec2fc91b9c0437d57581e6323e.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/81b268ec2fc91b9c0437d57581e6323e.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/81b268ec2fc91b9c0437d57581e6323e.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造独属于你的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从卡组中抽取六角形地块并逐个放置，若将相同类型的地块拼成一组，还能获得额外积分。看着自己的世界茁壮成长，美丽的景观会真实地呈现在你眼前！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/7dced7d47643f68ea62f6eff0592f2a1.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/7dced7d47643f68ea62f6eff0592f2a1.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/7dced7d47643f68ea62f6eff0592f2a1.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过旋转地块改变它们的外观和布局，你还可以尝试扩展不同的地形类型并完成特殊目标——在这一过程中可以赚取大量积分！只要还剩地块没有放完，这个世界的大小就没有限制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/110ab0987036194bbce6197cfa99e65b.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/110ab0987036194bbce6197cfa99e65b.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/110ab0987036194bbce6197cfa99e65b.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造独特的地标</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过得分解锁多种地标，每种地标都会为你的世界增添独特的风格！你可以让沸腾的火山拔地而起，让闹鬼的拖拉机在田野驰骋，还可以邀请隐居的女巫在森林中安家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/3700f4078b66e24751eb1f4989a0d0eb.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 /></span>在地标周围搭建合适的景观，可以赢得更多地块，让你有更多潜力建造庞大的王国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/afea482938154520037b7aba39370d0d.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/afea482938154520037b7aba39370d0d.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/afea482938154520037b7aba39370d0d.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迎接怪物访客</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在开疆拓土的过程中发现各种传送门，将它与对应的环境相连接，就可以吸引各种怪物进入你的王国。每种怪物都有形状特别的栖息地，放置这些栖息地，你就可以看到他们愉快玩耍了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/cd3087345a4b3a4d69443b507ba87bf6.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/cd3087345a4b3a4d69443b507ba87bf6.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/cd3087345a4b3a4d69443b507ba87bf6.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一起登上幽灵火车！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的世界中编织铁路网，利用交叉口扩展其范围，让幽灵火车去到王国的各个角落！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/faecb5feedd7b3e305deac54cdd201e2.poster.avif?t=1763464159\" width=590 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/faecb5feedd7b3e305deac54cdd201e2.webm?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010170/extras/faecb5feedd7b3e305deac54cdd201e2.mp4?t=1763464159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不止这些！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁 40 多个独特的地标</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇见狼人、雪人、稻草人等怪物朋友</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在创意模式中无拘无束地建造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在困难模式中挑战自我</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友比拼，争夺榜首</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多惊喜等着你！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你有什么想法？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最初的社区反馈之后，我们已经在着手开发一些新功能，为游戏带来激动人心的新变化。欢迎来社区参与讨论——我们期待听到广大玩家的心声！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
